# Episode Release Runbook (.mrd)

## Purpose
Checklist for manual or automated release of a new podcast episode.

## Checklist
- [ ] Confirm story, audio, description, and artwork are generated and stored
- [ ] Validate episode appears in the web app (UI/UX check)
- [ ] Validate episode appears in the RSS feed (and passes RSS validator)
- [ ] Announce or syndicate the new episode (if desired)
- [ ] Archive or back up assets as needed

## Notes
- Use this checklist for both automated and manual releases to ensure nothing is missed.
